    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thou art the joy of the heav--en-ly or-ders found on high, and of us men up-on earth, a strong help and pro-tec-tion. Save us, O pure Vir-gin and Moth--er of God, as we flee un-to thee in faith; for af-ter God, we have set all our hope on thee, seek-ing ref-uge in thy might--y__ strength."
